# .searchignore — patterns for memory_search.py:discover_files() to skip
#
# Syntax: gitignore-style glob patterns (one per line, # for comments).
# Files matching ANY pattern AND older than SEARCHIGNORE_AGE_DAYS (default 30
# days, set in scripts/memory_search.py) are excluded from indexing.
#
# Hot files matching a pattern are still indexed; only cold archives drop.
# Author: Code-memory (BIAV-SC batch 1 dispatch, 2026-05-03)

# Session digests — verbose verbatim conversation logs.
# Recent ones stay (active reference); older than 30 days drop into cold tier.
memory/session-digests/*.md
memory/session-digests/*.meta.json

# Dream journals — daily phase-1 reports. Older than 30 days are stale.
memory/dreams/*.json
memory/dreams/access-log/*.json
